Root Entity (Scene Root)
├── GameManager (Entity)
│   ├── GameLogicComponent (gameManager.js)
│   └── ScoreboardUI (HTML UI Container - Updates handled by GameLogicComponent)
├── SantaSleigh (Entity)
│   ├── ModelComponent (GLTF Model for Santa's Sleigh)
│   ├── ColliderComponent (BoxCollider for collision detection)
│   └── DropController (Handles dropping items, attached to button actions)
├── CoalButton (UI Entity)
│   ├── UIComponent (2D Button - "Drop Coal")
│   └── ButtonLogic (JS logic for handling coal drop event)
├── GiftButton (UI Entity)
│   ├── UIComponent (2D Button - "Drop Gift")
│   └── ButtonLogic (JS logic for handling gift drop event)
├── HouseContainer (Entity)
│   ├── RedRoofHouse1 (Entity)
│   │   ├── ModelComponent (GLTF Model for Red Roof House)
│   │   └── ColliderComponent (BoxCollider to detect drops)
│   ├── GreenRoofHouse1 (Entity)
│   │   ├── ModelComponent (GLTF Model for Green Roof House)
│   │   └── ColliderComponent (BoxCollider to detect drops)
│   └── (Other houses with similar components)
├── ObstacleContainer (Entity)
│   ├── BlueHouse (Entity)
│   │   ├── ModelComponent (GLTF Model for Blue House)
│   │   └── ColliderComponent (BoxCollider for collision detection)
│   └── (Other obstacles with similar components)
├── DroppedItemContainer (Entity)
│   ├── DroppedCoal (Entity - Dynamically Created)
│   │   ├── ModelComponent (GLTF Model for Coal)
│   │   ├── ColliderComponent (SphereCollider for collision detection)
│   │   └── PhysicsComponent (Gravity applied during fall)
│   └── DroppedGift (Entity - Dynamically Created)
│       ├── ModelComponent (GLTF Model for Gift)
│       ├── ColliderComponent (SphereCollider for collision detection)
│       └── PhysicsComponent (Gravity applied during fall)
├── Background (Entity)
│   ├── ModelComponent (Background Model - Ground Plane or Skybox)
│   └── GroundController (Custom Component from GroundController.js - handles movement and looping)
└── AudioController (Entity)
    ├── AudioComponent (Handles all game-related sounds)
    ├── DropSound (Drop sound event)
    ├── MatchSound (Match success sound event)
    ├── MismatchSound (Mismatch sound event)
    ├── GameOverSound (Game Over sound event)
    └── LevelUpSound (Level up sound event)
